==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Aristate
<hw>A*ris"tate</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>aristatus</ets>, fr. <ets>arista</ets>. See <er>Arista</er>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Having a pointed, beardlike process,
as the glumes of wheat; awned.</def> <rj><au>Gray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Having a slender, sharp, or
spinelike tip.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Aristocracy</ent>⟦br⟧
